  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-48 is-title1-48 is-title-bold\">「<b>星媽Q&amp;A Part1</b>」</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">社團已經來到超過3000位社員，也有新社員陸續加入，為了讓大家盡快增進對星媽社團的了解，從今天起，星媽不定期推出「星媽Q&amp;A」，也同步收錄在社團「星媽Q&amp;A社員必看喔」主題區中，請大家要一起關注！<br />\n<br />\n這兩個多月創社來，很感謝大家的支持和愛護，每次收到爸爸媽媽們私訊來的感謝，我都相當感動，不過我一人的力量很有限，若覺得社團提供的資訊對您和孩子帶來幫助，懇請大家多多邀請一樣關注教育，熱愛數學的朋友和孩子們一起來星媽社團，一起共學共好喔！<br />\n<br />\n非常謝謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n圖文詳見以下臉書連結：<br />\n<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/750779752541379/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/750779752541379/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510546559-dd2cd654.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510526918-8815f544.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510579283-60d7f0dc.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510593817-ad29ab82.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510581033-a422c19d.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510636429-cabc6284.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510684692-63ecd5e9.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510633742-21fad3f4.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510689329-cf221196.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510619095-eea6e136.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510689884-ccf1869c.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510783983-c22d5e70.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510778068-17602c7f.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510797188-9d14b344.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510726075-cf010733.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510726068-61d7bb73.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510831331-6566a3c5.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023081413510849653-806f6647.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
